form.current-chamber: In the House of Representatives, U. S.,
form.official-title: Electing a Member to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

section.text: That the following named Member be, and is hereby, elected to the following standing committees of the House of Representatives:

committee-appointment-paragraph.header: Committee on Oversight and Government Reform:
committee-appointment-paragraph.text: Ms. Kelly of Illinois (to rank immediately after Ms. Duckworth).
